USR1CMDS.text:
<:-- ===== Source for ISPF command table SCU1CMDS ****************-->
<:doctype dm system>
<cmdtbl applid=USR1>
 <:-- ============================================================ -->
 <:-- Generated 28 Jan 2016 by IBM's ISPCMDTB EXEC.                -->
 <:-- ============================================================ -->
 <:--          Compile to your ISPPROF DSN using IBM's ISPDTLC     -->
 <:-- ============================================================ -->
 <:--          Alias entries must preceed other entries.           -->
 <:-- ============================================================ -->
 <:-- ================================================ BROWSE ==== -->
  <cmd name=BRowse
      altdescr="ISPF Browse w/Point-N-Shoot capability">BR<T>owse
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%BR &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(BROWSE)">

  <:-- =============================================== ACMDLIST == -->
  <cmd name=CMDList
      altdescr="Display the selected ISPF Command List">CMDL<T>ist
    <cmdact action=
        "SELECT CMD(%CMDLIST &ZPARM) SCRNAME(CMDLIST)">

  <:-- =============================================== CMDMAINT == -->
  <cmd name=CMDMaint
      altdescr="Maintain the ISPF CMDs List for given Profile">CMDM<T>aint
    <cmdact action=
           "SELECT CMD(%CMDMAINT &ZPARM) SUSPEND SCRNAME(CMDMAINT)">

 <:-- ================================================ CNTL ====== -->
  <cmd name=CNTL
      altdescr="Edit ISPF Temporary (File Tayloring) Dataset">
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%CNTL &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(CNTL)">

  <:-- =============================================== DATEX ===== -->
  <cmd name=DATEX
      altdescr="Display Date Information">
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%DATEX &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP)">

 <:-- ================================================ EDIT ====== -->
  <cmd name=EDit
      altdescr="ISPF Edit w/Point-N-Shoot capability">ED<T>it
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%ED &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(EDIT)">

  <:-- =============================================== ISPCCONF == -->
  <cmd name=ISPCConf
      altdescr="Start the ISPF Configuration Utility">ISPCC<T>onf
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%ISPCCONF &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP)">

  <:-- =============================================== ISPCMDTB == -->
  <cmd name=ISPCMdtb
      altdescr="Convert Opened CMD Table to DTL">ISPCM<T>dtb
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%ISPCMDTB &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISP)">

 <:-- ================================================ ISPFTEST == -->
  <cmd name=ISPFTest
      altdescr="ISPF Dialog Test Screens">ISPFT<T>est
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT PGM(ISPYXDR) PARM(&ZAPPLID) SCRNAME(ISPFTEST)">

  <:-- =============================================== JCL ======= -->
  <cmd name=JCL
      altdescr="Start Edit session on personal Z.CNTL library">
    <cmdact
       "SELECT CMD(%ED Z.CNTL(&ZPARM)) NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(JCL)">

  <:-- =============================================== JOBLIBS === -->
  <cmd name=JOBlibs
      altdescr="Member Utility against STC JOB Libraries">JOB<T>libs
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%EDITLIBS JOBLIBS MEM(&ZPARM))
                           SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(JOBLIBS)">

 <:-- ================================================ LISTCAT === -->
  <cmd name=LISTCat
      altdescr="ListCat Utility">LISTC<T>at
    <cmdact
       "SELECT CMD(%TSOVIEW LISTC ENT(&ZPARM)) NEWAPPL(ISP) MODE(LISTC)">

  <:-- =============================================== MAN ===== -->
  <cmd name=MAN
      altdescr="Unix Man Page -- Display Unix Man Page for ...">MAN
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT CMD(%MAN &ZPARM) SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(USSMAN)">

  <:-- =============================================== MLCMD ===== -->
  <cmd name=MLCmd
      altdescr="Mbr List Command -- Al's Member List ...">MLC<T>md
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT CMD(%ML &ZPARM) SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(MemList)">

  <:-- =============================================== MUCMD ===== -->
  <cmd name=MUcmd
      altdescr="MuckUp Command -- Al's Member Utility ...">MU<T>cmd
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT CMD(%MU &ZPARM) SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(MuckUp)">

  <:-- =============================================== MYDSNS ==== -->
  <cmd name=MYDSNS
      altdescr="List the Datasets under my UserID">MYD<T>sns
    <cmdact action="SELECT PGM(ISRDSLST) PARM(DSL *&ZPARM)
                    SUSPEND SCRNAME(MYDSNS) NEWAPPL(ISR)">

  <:-- =============================================== PARMLIBS == -->
  <cmd name=PARMlibs
      altdescr="Member Utility against System PARMLIB Members">PARM<T>libs
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%EDITLIBS PARMLIBS MEM(&ZPARM))
                           SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(PARMLIBS)">

  <:-- =============================================== PROCLIBS == -->
  <cmd name=PROClibs
      altdescr="Member Utility against STC PROC Libraries">PROC<T>libs
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%EDITLIBS PROCLIBS MEM(&ZPARM))
                           SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(PROCLIBS)">

  <:-- =============================================== PROCMSTR == -->
  <cmd name=PROCMstr
      altdescr="Member Utility against STC sub=MSTR Libraries">PROCM<T>str
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%EDITLIBS PROCMSTR MEM(&ZPARM))
                           SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(PROCMSTR)">

 <:-- ================================================ REXXTRY === -->
  <cmd name=REXXtry
      altdescr="Try a REXX Code Snippet.">REXX<T>try
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%REXXTRY &ZPARM) SCRNAME(REXXTRY)">

 <:-- ================================================ SETVAR === -->
  <cmd name=SETVar
        altdescr="Set an ISPF Varialble Value">SETV<T>ar
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%SETVAR &ZPARM)">

 <:-- ================================================ SHOWVAR === -->
  <cmd name=SHOWVar
        altdescr="Show an ISPF Variable Value">SHOWV<T>ar
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%SHOWVAR &ZPARM)">

  <:-- =============================================== STCLIBS === -->
  <cmd name=STClibs
      altdescr="Member Utility against all STC Libraries">STC<T>libs
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%EDITLIBS STCLIBS MEM(&ZPARM))
                           SUSPEND NEWAPPL(ISP) SCRNAME(STCLIBS)">

 <:-- ================================================ TIME ====== -->
  <cmd name=TIME
      altdescr="Display current Date & Time.">
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%ISPTIME &ZPARM)">

 <:-- ================================================ TSOView === -->
  <cmd name=TSOView
      altdescr="TSO Full-screen Command">TSOV<T>iew
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT CMD(%TSOVIEW &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISR) SCRNAME(TSOVIEW)">

 <:-- ================================================ VIEW ====== -->
  <cmd name=VIew
      altdescr="ISPF View w/Point-N-Shoot capability">VI<T>ew
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%VW &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISR) SCRNAME(View)">

 <:-- ================================================ VW ======== -->
  <cmd name=VW
      altdescr="ISPF View w/Point-N-Shoot capability">
    <cmdact action="SELECT CMD(%VW &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISR) SCRNAME(VW)">

 <:-- ================================================ ZSTART ==== -->
  <cmd name=ZSTART
      altdescr="Set ISPF ZSTART Variable to use in ISPF Startup">
    <cmdact action=
       "SELECT CMD(%ZSTART &ZPARM) NEWAPPL(ISR) SCRNAME(ZSTART)">

</cmdtbl>
